snippet: The Justice Department says Attorney General Eric Holder will travel to Overland Park, Kan., on Thursday to pay tribute to the victims of the shootings at two Jewish community sites....

headline.print_headline: Holder to Deliver Remarks in Overland Park
headline.main: Holder to Deliver Remarks in Overland Park

lead_paragraph: The Justice Department says Attorney General Eric Holder will travel to Overland Park, Kan., on Thursday to pay tribute to the victims of the shootings at two Jewish community sites.
